@startuml
title UC03 Credential user completes device flow with a user code

actor "Credential user" as User
participant "Client application" as Client
participant "Enki Gate UI" as UI
participant "Enki Gate API" as API
database "Firestore" as Firestore
participant "Cloud Logging" as Logging

Client -> API: Start device flow
API -> Firestore: Create the device flow
Firestore --> API: deviceCode / userCode
API --> Client: deviceCode / userCode / verification URI

User -> UI: Open the Enki Gate device-flow page
UI --> User: Prompt for Google sign-in
User -> UI: Sign in with Google
User -> UI: Enter the user code
UI -> API: Request user-code validation
API -> Firestore: Look up the device flow
Firestore --> API: Device-flow state
API --> UI: Return the validation result
UI -> Firestore: Load credentials available to the signed-in user
Firestore --> UI: Selectable credential list
UI --> User: Show the credential list

User -> UI: Select the credential to use
UI -> API: Request device-flow authorization
API -> Firestore: Update the device flow to authorized
Firestore --> API: Update complete
API -> Logging: Record device-flow authorization
API --> UI: Return the completion result
UI --> User: Show completion

loop polling
  Client -> API: Check the device-flow state
  API -> Firestore: Read the device flow
  Firestore --> API: pending or authorized

  alt pending
    API --> Client: pending
  else authorized
    API -> Firestore: Record the token issuance
    Firestore --> API: Recording complete
    API -> Firestore: Update the device flow to completed
    Firestore --> API: Update complete
    API -> Logging: Record token issuance
    API --> Client: Return the gateway token
  end
end
@enduml
